#ROOM
Vnum     14000
Name     &YThe Gates of Ironforge&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     Massive bronze doors, each standing forty feet tall and inscribed with
the history of the dwarven people, mark the entrance to &YIronforge&d. The
doors stand perpetually open in welcome to Alliance travelers, though
they could be sealed in moments should the mountain come under attack.
Mountaineers stand vigilant on either side, their rifles gleaming. The
road from &CDun Morogh&d lies to the &Ysouth&d, while the &WCommons&d await
within to the &Ynorth&d.
~
Flags    nomob~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14001
Desc      The great entry hall leads into the Commons.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14700
Desc      The snow-covered road leads to Dun Morogh.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14000 2 14000
  Reset E 1 14000 1 16
  Reset E 1 14021 1 12
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14001
Name     &WThe Commons - Entry Hall&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You enter the vast underground city of &YIronforge&d, carved from the
living rock of the mountain itself. The ceiling arches high overhead,
supported by massive pillars carved with images of dwarven heroes. Braziers
filled with burning coal light the hall with a warm orange glow. The
&WCommons&d, Ironforge's main thoroughfare, stretches before you to the
&Ynorth&d. The great gates lie to the &Ysouth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14002
Desc      The Commons continues deeper into the city.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14000
Desc      The great gates lead outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14001 2 14001
  Reset E 1 14001 1 16
  Reset E 1 14004 1 4
Reset M 0 14020 3 14001
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14002
Name     &WThe Commons - Central Plaza&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The heart of Ironforge's Commons bustles with activity. Dwarves, gnomes,
and Alliance visitors from distant lands mingle here, conducting business
and sharing news. A massive statue of &WKing Modimus Anvilmar&d, founder of
the united dwarven nation, dominates the center of the plaza. Tunnels
branch in all directions—&Ynorth&d toward the &RGreat Forge&d, &Yeast&d to the
&CMystic Ward&d, &Ywest&d to the &YMilitary Ward&d, and &Ysouth&d back toward
the gates.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14010
Desc      The heat of the Great Forge beckons.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14030
Desc      The Mystic Ward lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14001
Desc      The entry hall lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14050
Desc      The Military Ward lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14020 5 14002
Reset M 0 14019 2 14002
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14003
Name     &WThe Commons - Eastern Walk&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This wide walkway connects the central plaza to the eastern districts
of Ironforge. Merchant stalls line the walls, selling everything from
fresh bread to exotic gems. The smell of baking and metalwork mingles
in the warm air. The plaza lies to the &Ywest&d, and the walk continues
&Yeast&d toward the bank. A tavern entrance is visible to the &Ynorth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14004
Desc      The sign of the Stonefire Tavern hangs above a doorway.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14006
Desc      The walk continues toward the Vault.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14002
Desc      The central plaza lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14019 2 14003
Reset M 0 14020 3 14003
Reset O 0 14010 3 14003
Reset O 0 14011 2 14003
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14004
Name     &YThe Stonefire Tavern&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     Warmth and laughter fill this beloved dwarven tavern. A roaring fire
crackles in a massive stone hearth, and the smell of roasting meat and
spilled ale permeates everything. Sturdy wooden tables are crowded with
dwarves telling tales and singing bawdy songs. A long bar runs along the
&Yeast&d wall, and a staircase leads &Yup&d to guest rooms.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14003
Desc      The Commons lies outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14005
Desc      The bar area lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    14008
Desc      A staircase leads to the upper rooms.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14004 1 14004
Reset M 0 14005 2 14004
Reset M 0 14020 4 14004
Reset O 0 14008 5 14004
Reset O 0 14009 5 14004
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14005
Name     &YThe Stonefire Tavern - Bar&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     A long bar of polished granite dominates this section of the tavern.
Barrels of ale are stacked behind the counter, and an impressive array
of mugs, tankards, and bottles line the shelves. The innkeeper presides
over this domain with cheerful efficiency, keeping drinks flowing and
patrons happy.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14004
Desc      The main tavern room lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 14008 10 14005
Reset O 0 14009 10 14005
Reset O 0 14012 3 14005
Reset O 0 14013 2 14005
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14006
Name     &WThe Commons - The Vault&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The wide corridor opens into a grand chamber dominated by the imposing
facade of &YThe Vault&d, Ironforge's legendary bank. Massive iron doors
stand open during business hours, revealing glimpses of the secure rooms
within. Armed guards watch everyone with suspicious eyes. The walk
continues &Ywest&d, and the bank entrance is to the &Ynorth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14007
Desc      Heavy doors lead into the Vault.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14003
Desc      The eastern walk leads back to the plaza.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14001 2 14006
  Reset E 1 14001 1 16
  Reset E 1 14003 1 15
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14007
Name     &YThe Vault of Ironforge&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     Cool air and the gleam of gold greet you inside Ironforge's legendary
Vault. Teller windows of reinforced iron line the walls, each manned by
a sharp-eyed banker. Behind them, the massive vault doors of solid mithril
stand partially visible, their locks said to be unpickable. The wealth of
the Alliance is safeguarded here.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14006
Desc      The Commons lies outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14007 2 14007
Reset O 0 14017 1 14007
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14008
Name     &YThe Stonefire Tavern - Upper Landing&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     A narrow hallway runs the length of the tavern's upper floor. Doors to
modest guest rooms line both walls, and the sounds of snoring and muffled
conversation drift through the wood. A window at the far end overlooks
the Commons below. The stairs lead &Ydown&d to the main tavern.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    14004
Desc      The stairs lead down to the tavern.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14009
Name     &WThe Commons - Auction House&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The clamor of commerce fills this busy chamber. Auctioneers call out
bids from raised platforms, while buyers and sellers haggle over goods
from across the Alliance. Notice boards cover the walls, advertising
everything from rare weapons to mundane supplies. The central plaza lies
to the &Ysouth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14002
Desc      The central plaza lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14006 1 14009
Reset M 0 14019 3 14009
Reset M 0 14020 4 14009
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14010
Name     &RThe Great Forge - Southern Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wave of heat washes over you as you approach the &RGreat Forge&d, the
massive lava pit at the very heart of Ironforge. The air shimmers, and
the orange glow of molten rock illuminates everything with fierce light.
This ancient forge has burned since the founding of the city, and its
flames have crafted countless legendary weapons. The path circles the
forge to the &Yeast&d and &Ywest&d. The Commons lies &Ysouth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14011
Desc      The path circles the forge to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14002
Desc      The cooler Commons lie to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14014
Desc      The path circles the forge to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14013 2 14010
Reset M 0 14020 3 14010
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14011
Name     &RThe Great Forge - Eastern Ring&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Smiths work at anvils along the outer wall, the clanging of their hammers
creating a constant rhythm. Sparks fly as metal is shaped and cooled. The
lava pit bubbles and churns to your &Ywest&d, separated only by a low stone
wall. The ring continues &Ynorth&d and &Ysouth&d, and a smithy lies to the
&Yeast&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14012
Desc      The ring continues north.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14015
Desc      A master smithy lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14010
Desc      The southern entrance lies behind you.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14008 1 14011
Reset M 0 14013 1 14011
Reset O 0 14015 3 14011
Reset O 0 14016 3 14011
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14012
Name     &RThe Great Forge - Northern Ring&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The northern section of the ring offers a view straight down into the
churning lava below. Platforms extend out over the pit, used by master
smiths who require the most intense heat for their finest works. The
heat here is almost unbearable. The High Seat lies to the &Ynorth&d, and
the ring continues &Yeast&d and &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14020
Desc      The High Seat of Ironforge lies beyond.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14011
Desc      The ring continues to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14013
Desc      The ring continues to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14008 1 14012
Reset M 0 14020 2 14012
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14013
Name     &RThe Great Forge - Western Ring&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     More workshops line the walls here, specializing in armor and shields.
Apprentice smiths pump massive bellows, feeding air to the forges. Racks
of completed works—breastplates, helms, gauntlets—line the walls, awaiting
their owners. The ring continues &Ynorth&d and &Ysouth&d, and a workshop
entrance lies to the &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14012
Desc      The ring continues north.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14014
Desc      The ring continues south.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
