Reset O 0 14006 2 14013
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14014
Name     &RThe Great Forge - Southwest Ring&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The circular path continues here, the ever-present heat and glow of the
forge dominating everything. Dwarven craftsmen take pride in working
closest to the ancient flames, and the finest masters have their stations
nearest the pit. The path continues &Ynorth&d and &Yeast&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14013
Desc      The ring continues north.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14010
Desc      The southern entrance lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
