Reset M 0 14020 2 14014
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14015
Name     &YForgemaster Thragrim's Smithy&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This is the personal workshop of &WForgemaster Thragrim&d, one of the
finest weaponsmiths in all of Khaz Modan. Half-finished blades hang on
racks, and a private forge burns hot against the far wall. The quality
of work here is evident in every gleaming edge and perfect weld. The
master himself works at his anvil, ignoring all distractions.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14011
Desc      The forge ring lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14008 1 14015
Reset O 0 14001 1 14015
Reset O 0 14002 1 14015
Reset O 0 14014 1 14015
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14016
Name     &YIronforge Armory Workshop&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Heavy armor dominates this workshop. Suits of plate hang on stands,
awaiting final fitting. Shields lean against every wall, bearing the
crests of various dwarven clans. The armorers here take immense pride
in crafting protection that has saved countless lives.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14013
Desc      The forge ring lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
