#ROOM
Vnum     14020
Name     &WThe High Seat - Antechamber&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     You enter the antechamber of the &WHigh Seat&d, the throne room of
Ironforge's king. Royal guards in ceremonial armor stand at attention,
their eyes watching every visitor. Banners bearing the Bronzebeard crest
hang from the walls—a mighty anvil beneath a crown of stone. The throne
room lies to the &Ynorth&d, and the Great Forge lies &Ysouth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14021
Desc      The throne room awaits beyond.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14012
Desc      The Great Forge lies to the south.
~
