#ROOM
Vnum     14021
Name     &WThe High Seat - Throne Room&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     The throne room of Ironforge is a chamber of breathtaking grandeur.
Massive pillars carved with the complete history of the dwarven people
support a ceiling lost in shadow. At the far end, upon a throne of
solid mithril, sits &WKing Magni Bronzebeard&d himself, ruler of all
Ironforge. Advisors and thanes stand nearby, attending to the business
of the kingdom. A war room lies to the &Yeast&d, and the Senate chamber
is to the &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14022
Desc      The war room lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14020
Desc      The antechamber lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14023
Desc      The Senate chamber lies to the west.
~
