#ROOM
Vnum     14022
Name     &WThe High Seat - War Room&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     A massive stone table dominates this chamber, its surface carved into a
detailed map of Khaz Modan and the surrounding regions. Miniature figures
representing troop positions are scattered across the map. Military
commanders debate strategy in hushed, urgent tones. Battle plans and
intelligence reports cover the walls.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14021
Desc      The throne room lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
