#ROOM
Vnum     14023
Name     &WThe High Seat - Senate Chamber&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     The Senate of Ironforge meets in this circular chamber. Stone benches
arranged in tiers surround a central speaking platform, where thanes
from every major clan gather to debate law and policy. The acoustics
are perfect—a whisper from the floor can be heard clearly in the highest
row.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14021
Desc      The throne room lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14021 4 14023
Reset M 0 14003 1 14023
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14030
Name     &CThe Mystic Ward - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air grows cooler and charged with arcane energy as you enter the
&CMystic Ward&d. Strange lights flicker in alcoves, and the faint hum of
magical wards vibrates through the stone. This district is home to
Ironforge's practitioners of the arcane arts—mages, warlocks, and priests
alike. The Commons lie to the &Ywest&d, and the ward continues &Yeast&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14031
Desc      The Mystic Ward continues deeper.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14002
Desc      The Commons lie to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14022 1 14030
Reset M 0 14020 2 14030
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14031
Name     &CThe Mystic Ward - Central Chamber&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Glowing runes are carved into the floor of this circular chamber, pulsing
with soft blue light. Bookshelves stuffed with ancient tomes line the
curved walls, and crystal orbs float in niches, displaying scenes from
distant lands. Mages practice incantations in hushed tones, and the smell
of incense and ozone fills the air. The &YHall of Mysteries&d lies &Ynorth&d,
and the &YTemple of Light&d is to the &Ysouth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14032
Desc      The Hall of Mysteries beckons.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14034
Desc      The Temple of Light lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14030
Desc      The ward entrance lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14022 2 14031
Reset M 0 14020 2 14031
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14032
Name     &CThe Hall of Mysteries&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This is the heart of arcane study in Ironforge. Apprentice mages practice
cantrips under the watchful eyes of masters, while senior wizards conduct
complex experiments in warded alcoves. Magical artifacts are displayed in
protective cases, their powers carefully contained. A portal chamber lies
to the &Ynorth&d, and a library is to the &Yeast&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14033
Desc      The portal chamber lies beyond.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14036
Desc      The arcane library lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14031
Desc      The central chamber lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14022 2 14032
Reset O 0 14020 1 14032
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14033
Name     &CThe Portal Chamber&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive stone ring dominates this chamber, its surface covered in
glowing runes. This is one of Ironforge's portal nexuses, allowing
instantaneous travel to distant cities for those with the skill to
activate it. Residual magical energy crackles in the air, making your
hair stand on end.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    14032
Desc      The Hall of Mysteries lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14022 1 14033
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14034
Name     &WThe Temple of Light&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     Soft golden light suffuses this serene temple dedicated to the Holy Light.
Rows of stone pews face an altar of white marble, upon which an eternal
flame burns without heat. Priests in white and gold robes tend to the
faithful, offering blessings and healing to those in need. The air smells
of candle wax and peace.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    14031
Desc      The Mystic Ward lies to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14035
Desc      The meditation chambers lie to the east.
~
