  Reset E 1 14005 1 7
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14035
Name     &WTemple Meditation Chambers&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     Small meditation cells line this quiet corridor, each providing a private
space for prayer and contemplation. Candles flicker in wall sconces, and
the distant sound of hymns drifts through the air. This is a place of
profound peace and spiritual reflection.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14034
Desc      The main temple lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14011 1 14035
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14036
Name     &CThe Arcane Library&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Floor-to-ceiling bookshelves fill this vast library, containing thousands
of volumes on every conceivable magical topic. Floating candles provide
illumination without risk of fire, and enchanted ladders slide along
tracks to reach the highest shelves. Scholars hunch over desks, taking
notes from ancient grimoires.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    14032
Desc      The Hall of Mysteries lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 14022 1 14036
Reset M 0 14012 1 14036
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     14050
Name     &YThe Military Ward - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The clash of weapons and shouts of drill sergeants fill the air as you
enter the &YMilitary Ward&d. This district houses Ironforge's standing army,
training facilities, and the offices of its military command. Soldiers
march in formation, and the smell of oil and leather is everywhere. The
Commons lie to the &Yeast&d, and the ward continues &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    14002
Desc      The Commons lie to the east.
~
