Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large open area has been carved from the rock, its floor covered in
packed sand. Dwarven warriors spar with practice weapons, their movements
precise and deadly. Weapon racks line the walls, and training dummies
bear the marks of countless strikes. The barracks lie &Ynorth&d, the
armory is &Ysouth&d, and the gryphon roost is to the &Ywest&d.
~
